instructions:

1.make a different folder 
2.put the main program there
3.run the program
4.niter number of dat file will be generated in the same folder on each run
5.open the gnuplot in the same folder and visualize.
6.if you want to run the program for the second time it will be better to delete the previous enormous number of dat files using following gnucmd...."$ find . -name "*.dat" -type f -delete"

7.you can run and visualize again and again just by using the previous steps.

thank you.
